# Styling (client)

- Tokens: `ink`, `bone`, `muted`, `line`, `tracking-luxe` — see `client/tailwind.config.ts`.
- Mobile-first breakpoints. Black / white minimal luxury.
- Avoid raw hex in components; use tokens.
- Keep focus styles visible for accessibility.
